encies and ATB-movement. The languages considered include English, German and Hebrew.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aGrammar, Comparative and generalxSyntax. 0aMinimalist theory (Linguistics). 0aParallelism (Linguistics). 4aATB-Bewegung. 4aDependenzgrammatik. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / Syntax.2bisacsh  aATB Movement.  aCriterial Freezing.  aLong-distance Dependencies.  aNested Dependencies.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1z978311076249508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE ENGLISH 2017z978311062526408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2017z9783110547887oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97831105201870 cprintz978311052012540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311052251840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110522518423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110522518/original  a978-3-11-062526-4  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE ENGLISH 2017b2017  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  a978-3-11-076249-5  DG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DSPb2017